# 
# CentOS 8 LedgerSMB Easy Installer
# By: STEVE ARBOUR 	Version: 1.0.0
#################################################################################
# 
# STEP REQUIRED: 
#
# INSTALL CENTOS 8 - SERVER NO GUI
# UNPACK THIS INSTALLER
# EDIT THE FILE CONFIGURATION
# MAKE THE INSTALLER EXECUTABLE (chmod ug+x install.sh)
# LAUNCH THE INSTALLER (./install.sh)
# 
# THIS SCRIPT REQUIRE:
#
# - AN EXTERNAL IP ADDRESS
# - A HOSTNAME THAT RESOLVE TO THAT IP ADDRESS
# - AN EMAIL ADDRESS FOR LETSENCRYPT TO USE.
#
#################################################################################
#
# WARNING: DO NOT PUT WWW IN THE HOSTNAME
# WE WANT TO USE example.com AND NOT www.example.com OR
# WE WANT TO USE subdomain.example.com AND NOT www.subdomain.example.com
#
#################################################################################
#
# WARNING : Please do not touch or operate the system during the installation, "
# it should reboot up to 5 times and may appear hanging out at boot because of "
# a pause that I introduce at each boot sequence with sleep timer setting."
# INSTALLER_SLEEP_ON_BOOT=15 
# (Default 15 seconds, you can rise this setting for slow server)"
#
#################################################################################